 Saturday. We just thought Sandown would suit him more. He\u2019s next year\u2019s chaser.\u201d\n\nGreg Wood\u2019s Tuesday tips\n\nExeter\n\n2.20 Midnight Request 2.50 Carnspindle 3.20 Gustav 3.50 Lower Hope Dandy 4.20 Baccalaureate 4.50 Mister Big\n\nNewcastle\n\n2.10 Airpur Desbois 2.40 Plus Jamais 3.10 Oishin 3.40 Two Smokin Barrels (nb) 4.10 Midnight Moss 4.40 Le Frank\n\nSouthwell\n\n2.00 Treaty Of Rome 2.30 Bridey\u2019s Lettuce 3.00 Pinwood 3.30 Shearian (nap) 4.00 Tasaaboq 4.30 Wimboldsley", 
